msgstr "Pitch Numberブロックは番号に対応した音高を再生します。例：0はC、7はG。"


#: js/blocks/PitchBlocks.js:1740
#: js/blocks/PitchBlocks.js:1786
#.TRANS: a numeric mapping of the notes in an octave based on the musical mode
#.TRANS: a numeric mapping of the notes in an octave based on the musical mode
